Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.31,0:00:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.23,0:00:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.79,0:00:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.26,0:00:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.19,0:01:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To the Final Battlefield!\N Dartz VS Yugi and Kaiba"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.03,0:01:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.83,0:01:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This building is about to collapse...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say what?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.42,0:01:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The elevator!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're screwed! There's nowhere left to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto-{\i1}sama{\i0}~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.78,0:02:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, Rafael?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.00,0:02:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.59,0:02:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yugi!\N -Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.77,0:02:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director! It's far too dangerous to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.27,0:02:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.33,0:03:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go, Yugi! Change your destiny with your own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.59,0:03:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.52,0:03:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael{\i0}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.54,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jump, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.17,0:04:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what Paradias {\i1}really{\i0} looks like...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean we were tricked by some sort of magic spell or something...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.49,0:04:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just us...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.03,0:04:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This entire city...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.20,0:04:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everyone in the entire world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.57,0:04:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Rafael...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.66,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.22,0:04:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A map!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where Dartz is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.30,0:04:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take us here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they working with Dartz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they asking us to follow them?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where they're taking us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Locusts?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.81,0:05:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A whole swarm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.66,0:05:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Look ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back! Back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.04,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not good! They've got us surrounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Becky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Come at me if you're gonna!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you people soldiers of Doma?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Kaiba, we have been keeping a close eye on Doma's movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of your people's actions as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.03,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.32,0:07:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are fully aware that Doma has been manipulating the world on a massive scale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Doma's influence has gone as far as to even medium federal taxes. They are beyond our call of duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't the authority to launch an attack against Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.75,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Doma really does have control over the major powers and their politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.51,0:07:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's shameful to say this, but the fate of the world rests with your group.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph! I never asked about your tax situation nor did I request for your authority from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.85,0:07:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, we can take you there halfway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.36,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we'll refuel your helicopter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We cannot proceed any further than this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.46,0:08:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a great number among us who pray for your success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmph... I appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My son is a {\i1}huge{\i0} fan of Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please protect the future of our children!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isono, start up the helicopter!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His map said it was around here somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's out of the question, Director!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.59,0:08:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We can't get any closer than this!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are the tornadoes inviting us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.90,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.66,0:09:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz is inside there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Doma's stronghold!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.46,0:09:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:44.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this oppressing aura?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I can feel it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.23,0:09:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.60,0:09:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys, stay right by our sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those must be the taken souls...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.43,0:10:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.72,0:10:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have waited for your arrival...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I am to gather souls harnessing strength on par with that of your own...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the birth of my God shall be indubitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "birth" you speak of is nothing but a massive headache!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.29,0:10:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O Sovereign Souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:11:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall prepare a special place for the both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the bullshit! We already took down the "Three Musketeers" you sent after us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! You're the only one left!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.94,0:11:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.61,0:11:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have certainly taken down my Musketeers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their souls were already planned offerings from the very start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just... too cruel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that alone will not suffice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am in need of your souls as well in order to complete the resurrection of my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz! Stop this pointless battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And return the souls you took away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.38,0:11:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way that will come to pass is if you are to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.22,0:11:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bear witness!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.21,0:12:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the source behind that oppressing aura.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.55,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey! Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.55,0:12:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's this many people trapped here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.55,0:12:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they're not just people from our present time...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.93,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.26,0:12:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is filled with souls collected over 10,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I myself am nothing more than a relic of this history.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.94,0:12:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.94,0:12:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi, nothing you say will get through to this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as Duels were originally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...this shall be a battle ritual where we\N place our very souls at the stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are to follow the way things were meant to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll be your opponent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Kaiba! I can't stand here and let you take him on by yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then as settlement...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I shall take both your souls at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.09,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh! Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.68,0:13:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you to tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.93,0:13:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.56,0:13:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Varon...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.11,0:13:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And me as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have something we must do!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.95,0:13:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.96,0:13:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I play a Ritual Magic from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.63,0:13:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Descent of White Dragon activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from my hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice Blood Vorse!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.18,0:13:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth! Knight of White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I activate his Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:14:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sacrificing Knight of White Dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.92,0:14:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unable to attack within the first turn of a match.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll end my turn with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here goes, Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.51,0:14:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Chaos Ritual from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I offer up Magnet Valkyrian as the sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.19,0:14:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I invoke upon the legendary warrior, Chaos Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And after setting up a reverse face-down card, I end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:14:57.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're awesome! Both my brother {\i1}and{\i0} Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They Summoned their Ace Monsters in just one turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very perceptive.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You both seem to have grasped the depth of who it is you are fighting against.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.17,0:15:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O great card born from the bowels of darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.47,0:15:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bestow upon them your almighty power!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His fighting spirit's no joke...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an outsider and I can feel it clear as day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.27,0:16:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.27,0:16:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I knew it...! He's no ordinary man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orichalcos Gigas!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.28,0:16:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let your guard down, Kaiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.33,0:16:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Monster has an incredibly strong power!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! If he didn't play a Monster of at least {\i1}this{\i0} level, things wouldn't be interesting in the slightest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall then deplete my Life...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and Special Summon Orichalcos Kyutora!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.30,0:16:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will finish off my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz, if you are truly the one\N composing Doma's actions,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this Duel's victory should also be within your grasp.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, you've only managed to Summon a couple of weak Monsters on your field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and victory has already fallen into {\i1}my{\i0} hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't the {\i1}slightest{\i0} idea as to what kind of Duelist you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you've forgotten one {\i1}very{\i0} important factor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:10.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you are now...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.75,0:17:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...taking on the strongest\N Duelists in existence as your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fuse the three Blue-Eyes from my hand and on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.28,0:17:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My ultimate servant!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.44,0:17:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.49,0:17:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Blue-Eyes Ultimate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi... If you're the True Duelist you say you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.11,0:17:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you should be able to call forth\N our {\i1}new{\i0} servant to kill him off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.50,0:17:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, I'll take it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.51,0:17:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.88,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This draw, Dartz, will shatter all of your ambitions in a single blow!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Fusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes Ultimate Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaos Soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.52,0:18:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate Fusion Summon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.28,0:18:16.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of Dragon Knight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing! It's got {\i1}5000{\i0} Attack Points!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.54,0:18:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My big brother and Yugi make the strongest tag pair in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, open!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.17,0:18:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.17,0:18:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When we attack holding stronger Attack than your Defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.42,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you receive the difference as direct damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.09,0:18:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got 3500 more Attack Points than the Defense Power of Dartz's Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.01,0:18:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that'll bring his Life right down to zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one attack alone will put an end to everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master of Dragon Knight!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Dartz!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.95,0:19:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Galaxy Crusher!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.15,0:19:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh. Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are unable to defeat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.37,0:19:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Space...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dartz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.02,0:20:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with this bogus illusion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.68,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not lose your cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your attack just now simply triggered the power of Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Within even a very fragment of the Orichalcos lies with it memories that far exceed that of human society.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.41,0:20:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dubbed the "World of Memories" that lies dormant within the Orichalcos.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.74,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Memories of the Orichalcos?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long before this age...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...everything in this world was born from darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.50,0:20:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us... Even the very planet we live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.71,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this world is once again headed back to the darkness... taking with it its own demise.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The citizens of this planet caused this and will now pay a very high price because of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the absolute way of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, it will take with it everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.98,0:20:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as human beings and their hearts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.15,0:21:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the threads of time shall embellish in the very darkness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying darkness of the heart is the way of life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our planet is beautiful...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps it is nothing short of a miracle that the universe could produce such an existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.25,0:21:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys unable to hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cries of this planet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.54,0:21:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The planet's... cries...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.76,0:21:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is the metropolis I once governed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As well as it is the city I destroyed with my very own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.48,0:21:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlantis!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atlantis was... such a beautiful city...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:44.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, that same path soon carved way for its destruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} have formed the ultimate tag team!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:22:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they managed to take down Dartz in one shot using the ultimate Monster, Master of Dragon Knight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.34,0:22:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.55,0:22:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of them disappeared in a huge flash of light!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.42,0:22:08.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} witness the memory of Atlantis's destruction within the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that hit didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.14,0:22:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how will they win this Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Tragedy of Atlantis"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.02,0:22:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.53,0:22:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.14,0:22:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.21,0:23:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.69,0:23:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.97,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.87,0:23:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.02,0:23:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.54,0:23:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
